<section>
<title>Description détaillée</title>

<para>Buffers all records until closing the handler and then pass them as batch.</para>

<para>This is useful for a MailHandler to send only one mail per request instead of sending one per log message.</para>

<para><formalpara><title>Auteur</title>

<para>Christophe Coevoet <link xlink:href="mailto:stof@notk.org">stof@notk.org</link></para>
</formalpara>
@phpstan-import-type Record from \Monolog\Logger </para>
</section>
